text: Iberia Airlines Flight 610 was a flight from Madrid to Bilbao, Spain on 19 February 1985. The Boeing 727-200 crashed near Bilbao due to pilot error. All 148 people on board died. == References == Category:Aviation accidents and incidents in the 1980s Category:Aviation accidents and incidents in Europe Category:1985 in Europe Category:1980s in Spain
title: Iberia Airlines Flight 610
